02:10:58.079 --> 02:10:59.669
could do us a favor: click the like

02:10:59.679 --> 02:11:01.430
button, subscribe, click the

02:11:01.440 --> 02:11:03.990
notification bell. I'm still

02:11:04.000 --> 02:11:05.350
pretty heavy with the

02:11:05.360 --> 02:11:07.189
anointing on me, so my mind—I'm trying

02:11:07.199 --> 02:11:08.709
to make it go 'woo'because I'm still in

02:11:08.719 --> 02:11:10.790
intercessory mode—but I

02:11:10.800 --> 02:11:14.149
need a break. I appreciate you all

02:11:14.159 --> 02:11:17.350
being here, I truly do. Thank you for

02:11:17.360 --> 02:11:18.470
being here,

02:11:18.480 --> 02:11:20.470
thank you for subscribing, thank you

02:11:20.480 --> 02:11:22.790
for clicking the notification bell. And

02:11:22.800 --> 02:11:25.109
the best is yet to come, folks.

02:11:25.119 --> 02:11:26.709
I'm just so grateful for every single

02:11:26.719 --> 02:11:29.750
one of you. Remember, put a smile on

02:11:29.760 --> 02:11:32.550
your face and a song in your heart.

02:11:32.560 --> 02:11:34.550
Jesus loves you so much, and we love you.

02:11:34.560 --> 02:11:35.990
God bless you all, and we'll see you

02:11:36.000 --> 02:11:39.840
again tomorrow. Bye-bye.

